OL,4,CCovid: Shed and garage offices pose
OL,5,Cinsurance risk
OL,6, A growing number of people expect to be
OL,7, working from converted sheds, garages
OL,8, and summerhouses as Covid changes our
OL,9, attitudes to home working, an insurer
OL,10, has said.
OL,12,FThe proportion planning a dedicated
OL,13,Foffice in the house is also growing,
OL,14,Faccording to the survey by Aviva.
OL,16,FIt appears some are moving away from
OL,17,Foperating from a sofa or armchair.
OL,19,FBut there are warnings that some may
OL,20,Fnot be covered by home insurance if
OL,21,Fsomething goes wrong.
